descriptionHtml:
Game saved at lvl 3 so you can use this beautiful Lunari character from the games start. I saved with original hair so she should look like this when you load the save. Apachi and Fallout 3 hair look great on her

mods used...
Lunari Race with option UNP then UNP custom.
RaceMenu and optional War Paints
Enhanced Character Edit
SKSE

Click required files (little disk icon on actions tab above download button) to get links for above mods. If you like the character please endorse those and not this file

These mods are installed and might be required
Pretty Face
UNP Blessed Body with BBP

For screenshots
RealVision ENB and lots of HD textures
